commits.author: Simon Willnauer
commits.sourceNew: /** * Increments the iteration to the next {@link BytesRef} in the iterator. * Returns the resulting {@link BytesRef} or null if the end of * the iterator is reached. The returned BytesRef may be re-used across calls * to next. After this method returns null, do not call it again: the results * are undefined. * * @return the next {@link BytesRef} in the iterator or null if * the end of the iterator is reached. * @throws IOException */ public BytesRef next() throws IOException;
